{"tid":154302,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"試食m記新包: 芝味蘑菇安格斯","createTime":"2017-03-13T08:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T01:00:47.000Z","uid":56508,"like":1,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc3eb2aa3ef3197d55a86675e76b81419976d98","tid":154302,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:06:52.000Z","msg":"去圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/13/152930_4be0e99410c12af2a01bfc7a5218e19b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F13%2F152930_4be0e99410c12af2a01bfc7a5218e19b.jpg&h=987d4b33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/13/152931_435d0061a290e8ae3b950353d357ccce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F13%2F152931_435d0061a290e8ae3b950353d357ccce.jpg&h=fecb6516&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/13/152932_6cf74be546a92608bcd95c8c23b47b77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F13%2F152932_6cf74be546a92608bcd95c8c23b47b77.jpg&h=99285225&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C0i9n4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC0i9n4p.jpg&h=99609c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊肉係厚就好厚 不過好難食<br />\n味道口感只不過係好多塊巨無霸嗰舊肉重疊放入口<br />\n個汁又好難食 同d蘑菇唔襯 <br />\n蘑菇乾淨淨<br />\n好撚難食<br />\n佢用咗隻新包 有d似餐包既感覺 無咩特別<br />\n評分: 2/10<br />\n1分俾包住個包張紙 幾方便唔會食到隻手污糟晒<br />\n另外嗰1分俾塊芝士既<br />\n<br />\n我唔會再食呢個垃圾包<br />\n還我心愛既板燒雞腿包！"},{"pid":"99799c1ddefe2ba8c1065b80dd39580b0f7be9d2","tid":154302,"uid":82384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:08:11.000Z","msg":"個餐幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9067c6055a097c00e3dd58dd3339f2a3ce2998","tid":154302,"uid