02,"uid":90552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:43:33.000Z","msg":"反而個新嘅火辣脆雞包幾好食.<br />\nJalapeno 辣椒 + 菠蘿 + 炸雞, 酸酸辣辣勁開胃. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47af7c2bba7737ac4b1acd5209b216a91c97d08","tid":154302,"uid":5762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而個新嘅火辣脆雞包幾好食.<br />\nJalapeno 辣椒 + 菠蘿 + 炸雞, 酸酸辣辣勁開胃. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但好多人話塊雞好乾 加埋嗰款包嘅質地乾上加乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事關我都1516想試呢款"},{"pid":"b57b727d3521f7945c096f95be34fe3e166a847e","tid":154302,"uid":27770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"點解我見到既係43蚊個餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n間間都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0bef9d9653499ccc1481a82d27f2a972b97084","tid":154302,"uid":73533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T09:20:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而個新嘅火辣脆雞包幾好食.<br />\nJalapeno 辣椒 + 菠蘿 + 炸雞, 酸酸辣辣勁開胃. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過真係唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c606bb3ce673e9ce96573de89ac5c5b5ef10a9","tid":154302,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T09:23:10.000Z","msg":"舊肉睇落dry到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783890bbf6b63909fbdaaec481933d8999a7d10c","tid":154302,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反而個新嘅火辣脆雞包幾好食.<br />\nJala